---
import Container from '../ui/Container.astro'
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-dark py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-24">

  <Container class="relative z-10 text-center">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2 class="mb-6 font-display text-display-sm tracking-tight text-white md:text-display-md">
        Pronto Para Estruturar Suas Vendas?
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mb-10 max-w-2xl font-sans text-body-lg text-gray-300">
        Escolha seu caminho e comece hoje mesmo a transformar vendas aleatórias em previsíveis.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
        <a href="/vss">
          <button class="inline-flex h-14 w-full items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-lime px-8 font-display text-lg font-bold text-dark shadow-lg shadow-lime/20 transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:bg-lime/90 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-lime focus:ring-offset-2 sm:w-auto">
            Vendas Sem Segredos
          </button>
        </a>
        <a href="/#contato">
          <button class="inline-flex h-14 w-full items-center justify-center rounded-lg border-2 border-white px-8 font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:bg-white/20 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white focus:ring-offset-2 sm:w-auto">
            Falar com Joel
          </button>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-content {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out forwards;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
